---
title: Steakhouse Cheeseburger with Mushroom Gravy, Montreal Steak-spiced Potato Wedges and Zesty Mayo
description: Steakhouse flavours of saucy mushrooms and Montreal Steak Spice in a weeknight cheeseburger. Dunk the golden roasted potatoes into the zesty mayo too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steakhouse-cheeseburger-2411b6ee.jpg
